{{Databox|fr=Carl Friedrich Gauss}}'''Yuhan Kaṛl fridiritc guss''' (1777 - 1855) yan [[Tusnakt|usnak]] d [[Tasngama|usngam]] aliman, lli iskrn tadaka d tyafut ɣ idɣarn ad n tussna (tasinakt d Tasngama). Ar as aqqran s "Agllid n usnakn" d "usnak lli kullu mqqurn zɣ assfal n ddunit". Guss ifka tugt i tasinakt d tussna, d iga ɣ inmɣurn n usnakn ɣ umzruy.

Ilul '''Guss''' ass n 30 bril 1777, izzri tamziyt nns ɣ [[Brunswick]] ɣ [[Lalman|uliman]], d nttat aɣ iɣra. 

Mas ur tɣri d ur tssn tizi n tlalit n iwis kaṛl, mac rad stt id ildi ntta d zɣ akud ann d aniɣ admzalalyn tmkfit nns ɣ tasinakt.

Ɣ sskʷil rad yaf afssay i mnnaw imukrisn ɣ tasinakt, mad lli rad issusm ''Duke n Brunswick'' lli rad t yazn s tzdawit n ''Collegium Carollinum'', ukan ar gis yaqqra gr 1792 d 1795, ar kiɣ immatti s tzdawit n ''Gottingen'', ukan ar daɣ yaqqra gr 1795 d 1798.

Ɣ isggʷasn dars iggʷran ɣ tzdawit, rad ifk '''Guss''' tugt n tdusi ɣ udɣar ad lli mu ikcm. Tugt n [[tmagunin]] rad tnt ismd, d tiyaḍ rad ffɣn-t s ubaraz, d ugidi n imukrisn lli mu yad ttanfn isinakn zɣ zikk rad asn yaf afssay.

Ittussan '''Guss''' mas iga argaz n tuwuru, d iɣama f unckk ann ar ass lliɣ immut ɣ 23 brayr 1855.

